title: Here Piggy Piggy
description: Uncle Grandpa chases his pig through the classic opening title sequence.

title: Uncle Grandpa 101
description: Uncle Grandpa teaches a classroom of Uncle Grandpas how to be Uncle Grandpa.

title: Mustache Tree
description: When Uncle Grandpa runs out of mustaches, he travels to the mustache tree to stock up. But upon arrival, it seems a new clan of elves have become very territorial over the tree. Now, Uncle Grandpa and the gang must fight in order to obtain a new 'stache.

title: Uncle Grandpa's Journey
description: Quick clips of false moments from the show's hilarious past and future.

title: Unboxing
description: Uncle Grandpa is making an internet video about unboxing a box.

title: Costume Crisis
description: Uncle Grandpa makes improvements to a kid's Halloween costume.

title: The Origin of Frankenstein
description: Dr. Frankenstein's creation is surprisingly very intelligent until Uncle Grandpa arrives.

title: Watermelon Gag
description: When Uncle Grandpa gets a watermelon stuck in his mouth, he is unable to ask for help and people interpret it as a comedy routine. As Uncle Grandpa's popularity rises, his friendships and morale suffer.

title: Duck Lips
description: After Uncle Grandpa molds her mouth into duck lips, a young girl must face the consequences of her new found popularity.

title: Spelling Bee
description: Uncle Grandpa is hosting a spelling bee game show. The contestants, Mr. Gus and Pizza Steve, are competing for the spelling bee trophy.

title: Spelling Bee
description: Uncle Grandpa is hosting a spelling bee game show. The contestants, Mr. Gus and Pizza Steve, are competing for the spelling bee trophy.

title: Trash Cat
description: Uncle Grandpa helps a cat who's afraid to take baths.

title: Behind the Scenes
description: A behind the scenes look at the cast and crew of Uncle Grandpa.

title: Will It Stick?
description: The guys have a contest to see what item will stick to the wall.

title: Uncle Dummy
description: Uncle Grandpa and Pizza Steve try to convince Mr. Gus that his ventriloquist dummy is alive.

title: Full Grown Pizza
description: Uncle Grandpa makes it hard for Pizza Steve to prove he's not a baby.

title: Broken Boogie
description: When the Boogie Man loses his mojo, Uncle Grandpa steps in to help.

title: Curiosities of Nature
description: In this collection of shorts, Uncle Grandpa and the gang goes on an incredible journey, plays a riveting new game, and get observed for a nature documentary.

title: Coolest Lunchbox
description: Uncle Grandpa and the crew are in high school and about to eat lunch when they compare who has the coolest lunchbox.

title: In the Clouds
description: Uncle Grandpa helps a boy get his head out of the clouds and focused on his history test.

title: The Case of the Missing Bike
description: Detective Frankenstein and Officer Tiny Miracle are on the case to help Katie find her stolen bicycle.

title: Wasteland
description: After Uncle Grandpa neglects his garbage duties, he embarks on a quest to save his friends from the overflowing pile of trash.

title: Bounce House
description: A kid's party is almost ruined, until UG arrives with his special Bounce House.

title: Tongue Tied
description: Uncle Grandpa helps a shy kid gain confidence.

title: No Farm No Foul!
description: Uncle Grandpa discovers a box of lost Uncle Grandpa episodes. The gang decides to watch the video reel.

title: Fear of Flying
description: Uncle grandpa helps a young boy overcome his fear of flying.

title: Nacho Cheese
description: Pizza Steve's father comes to visit the gang and almost immediately gets on their nerves with his over the top antics. Pizza Steve must get rid of his dad, and prove to himself that he doesn't need to live in his father's shadow any longer.

title: G'day Mornin'
description: Uncle grandpa goes to Australia where he must stop an out-of-control collecting kangaroo before he destroys the Earth.

title: Uncle Grandpa Ate My Homework
description: When Uncle Grandpa shows up and mistakenly eats a kid's Egyptian diorama for school, he helps the kid bring an actual pyramid to class, but accidentally unleashes an evil mummy on the world.

title: The Weird Zone
description: Pizza Steve has the crew do his bidding for fear of being transformed by his mind powers.
